Name:-
    Fake News Detection
Description:- 
    Take news detection is a process that involves analyzing news content to determine its truthfulness. It is a subtask of text classification, and is defined as the task of classifying news as real or fake.
Worked:-
    1.Import the lib
    2.Load the data
    3.Data Preprocessing
    4.EDA
    5.Text Cleaning and Preprocessing
    6.Text Classification
    7.Feature Selection
    8.Model Building
    9.Model Evaluation
Requirements:-
    python
    pandas
    numpy
    seaborn
    matplotlib
    sckit-learn
    nltk
    scpacy
    
